#: org.kde.kmenuedit.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KDE Menu Edit lets you edit how your apps are presented in application "
"launchers, such as Plasma's Application Launcher widget."
msgstr ""
"Menu Edit de KDE permitte te modifcar como tu applicationes es presentate in "
"lanceatores de app, come le widget Application Launcher (Lanceator de "
"application) de Plasma."
